This paper deals with the management of Wi-Fi networks, which falls under the category of computer networks (cs.NI). The paper also discusses optimization problems and algorithms for maximizing energy efficiency, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY) and information theory (cs.IT). Additionally, the paper discusses security issues related to network densification, which falls under the category of cryptography and security (cs.CR). Finally, the paper discusses the use of cloud-based management systems, which falls under the category of distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
